# The platform binaries are large (9-22 MB each) and would bloat the
# git repo. They're downloaded from GitHub Releases at publish time
# by scripts/npm-publish.sh.
#
# To publish a new version locally:
#   ./scripts/npm-publish.sh 0.1.0
#
# To skip the download (if you already have the binaries in place):
#   ./scripts/npm-publish.sh 0.1.0 --skip-download
@gilbertwong1996-ado-*/bin/ado
@gilbertwong1996-ado-*/bin/ado.exe
